{
  "stem": "3757.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, they took four squadrons together, and he gave a speech. 'You lousy Jews have to know that not one of them will come back alive.' This man was hang after the war-- Murai.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this-- this was the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was, of course, alone with-- with the other women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we formed kind of a chain, that if somebody has some news, call the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- because one-- one news give hope to the others.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the lucky one that I got always three, four times news about my husband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After that, he-- I got already that he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But believe that somehow one was-- and this I have to tell, because nobody could believe it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can never believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One Sunday, we had already the yellow star, and the building had the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One morning, a Sunday morning, came a man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was dressed like a-- like formal, for Sunday-- boots, and a nice coat, and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the super let him in, because it was not a Jewish man-- let him in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came and he said-- he rung the bell, and I-- I had my son on my arm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I opened the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he say, are you Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mautner?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "May I come in?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, come in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I brought some news about your husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I thought that he-- I started to shake, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I invited him come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sit down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he told me the following story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My son was in Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he managed to-- to take 10 men somehow to Turkey.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave me your address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he has a photograph and a letter for you-- to you.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
